properties.name: Fox Bar
properties.description: Posted by Bdolan2000 7520 Shawnee Mission Pkwy, Overland Park, KSThe only gay bar in the Kansas part of Kansas City -- the remaining 20-odd bars are all across the State line in Missouri. It\'s easy to miss the fox: the sign is tiny, the windows are dark, and it\'s in a strip mall next to an insurance company. A sign outside says \'private club for members only\'. Inside on a recent wednesday, the winter olympics were playing on tv, a mixed crowd played pool and drank .50 drafts, and a karaoke contest was gearing up.

properties.name: My kitties' papa...
properties.description: Posted by Bdolan2000244 n second ave, tucson azBuddy, rocky, and james, our three twin cats, were found hours old with their mom under a house here in Tucson. Years later, I browsed through the website of a cat shelter just a few blocks away and found this picture of a male cat who is a dead ringer for buddy. The resemblance is astounding, down to the smallest markings on his face. Of course, the odds are slim to none that this cat is really any relation, but if you\'re out there, kitty-daddy, here\'s to you.

properties.name: Somewhere on route 75...
properties.description: Posted by Bdolan2000Somewhere on a lonely stretch of highway approaching tampa, I snapped this pic of my grandmother\'s cat, Smokey, riding shotgun on the dashboard and high on kittykat valium. Turns out I gave her a double dose (a whole pill, rather than a half) by accident, and her back legs didn\'t work right for the next few days. We were driving grandma\'s van from Maine to Florida, so having Smokey extra-chillaxed for the two days of driving really didn\'t hurt.
